@{
    Layout = null;
}
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Privacy Policy — StormLead Pro</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-white text-slate-800 font-sans">
<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-12">
    <div class="mb-8">
        <a href="/" class="text-orange-500 text-sm hover:underline">← StormLead Pro</a>
    </div>

    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mb-8">Effective Date: April 29, 2025 &nbsp;|&nbsp; Last Updated: April 29, 2025</p>

    <div class="prose prose-slate max-w-none space-y-6 text-sm leading-relaxed">

        <section>
            <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">1. Who We Are</h2>
            <p>StormLead Pro ("we," "us," or "our") is operated by Ennis Lodge 369 and accessible at <strong>stormlead.pro</strong>. We provide storm-damage lead generation tools for roofing contractors.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">2. Information We Collect</h2>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
                <li><strong>Account information:</strong> name, email address, and authentication credentials when you sign in via Google or Microsoft.</li>
                <li><strong>Usage data:</strong> pages visited, searches performed, leads saved, and feature interactions.</li>
                <li><strong>Property data:</strong> addresses and parcel information searched or saved within the platform.</li>
                <li><strong>SMS opt-in data:</strong> if you respond to a storm-damage outreach SMS, we record your phone number and response to facilitate a roofing inspection inquiry.</li>
                <li><strong>Device and log data:</strong> IP address, browser type, and request logs for security and debugging purposes.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
                <li>To provide and improve the StormLead Pro platform.</li>
                <li>To send SMS messages related to storm damage assessments and roofing inspections when you have opted in.</li>
                <li>To authenticate your account and maintain session security.</li>
                <li>To comply with applicable laws and regulations.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">4. SMS Messaging</h2>
            <p>If you receive an SMS from StormLead Pro and reply, your phone number and response are stored solely for the purpose of connecting you with a licensed roofing contractor regarding storm damage to your property. <strong>We do not sell, share, or transfer your phone number or SMS responses to any third party for marketing purposes.</strong> You may opt out at any time by replying <strong>STOP</strong> to any message. For help, reply <strong>HELP</strong>.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">5. Data Sharing</h2>
            <p>We do not sell your personal information. We do not share your information with third parties for their own marketing purposes. We may share information only in the following limited circumstances:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
                <li>With service providers who process data on our behalf (e.g., Twilio for SMS delivery, Google Maps for geocoding) under confidentiality agreements.</li>
                <li>If required by law, court order, or governmental authority.</li>
                <li>To protect the rights, property, or safety of StormLead Pro, our users, or the public.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">6. Data Retention</h2>
            <p>We retain your data for as long as your account is active or as needed to provide services. SMS contact records are retained for up to 12 months. You may request deletion of your data by contacting us at the address below.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">7. Security</h2>
            <p>We use industry-standard security measures including HTTPS encryption, secure cookie handling, and access controls to protect your data.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">8. Your Rights</h2>
            <p>Depending on your jurisdiction, you may have the right to access, correct, or delete personal information we hold about you. To exercise these rights, contact us at <strong>support&#64;stormlead.pro</strong>.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
            <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will post the updated policy on this page with a revised effective date.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">10. Contact Us</h2>
            <p>For privacy-related questions, contact us at:<br />
            <strong>StormLead Pro</strong><br />
            Email: <a href="mailto:support@stormlead.pro" class="text-orange-500 hover:underline">support&#64;stormlead.pro</a><br />
            Website: <a href="https://stormlead.pro" class="text-orange-500 hover:underline">stormlead.pro</a></p>
        </section>

    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
